li>\n<li><strong>Regencell Bioscience Holdings Limited</strong> <span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NASDAQ\" data-ticker=\"RGC\" style=\"display:inline-block\">RGC</span> gained 7.7% to $689.00.</li>\n<li>A<strong>eroVironment, Inc</strong>. <span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NASDAQ\" data-ticker=\"AVAV\" style=\"display:inline-block\">AVAV</span> gained 6.6% to $198.94. AeroVironment will report its financial results for the fourth quarter after the market closes on Tuesday, June 24.</li>\n</ul><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\"><strong>Now Read This: </strong></p><!--/$--><!--$--><ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.benzinga.com/analyst-stock-ratings/analyst-color/25/06/45789751/jim-cramer-likes-dominion-energy-but-isnt-a-fan-of-this-real-estate-stock\" target=\"_blank\">Jim Cramer Likes Dominion Energy, But Isn’t ‘A Fan’ Of This Real Estate Stock</a></strong> </li>\n</ul><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">Photo via Shutterstock</p><!--/$--><!--$--><div><div><div class=\"bz-campaign bz-campaign-bottom-45815263\" data-nosnippet=\"true\"><div class=\"sc-c014f608-0 kUPEDz skeleton min-h-[inherit] animate-pulse variant\" role=\"status\"><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div></div><div class=\"flex sm:hidden flex-col\"><div class=\"sc-c014f608-0 kUPEDz skeleton min-h-[inherit] animate-pulse variant\" role=\"status\"><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--/$--></div></div>",
